  "html": "<div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>ἐπὶ ἀμφιπόλου ἐν Συρακούσαις <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἄπρου Σεξστίου Αὐγουρείνου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἄπρου\">Ἄπρου</span>  <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Σεξστίου\">Σεξστίου</span>  <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Αὐγουρείνου\">Αὐγουρείνου</span></span>  <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>ἱερείας δὲ παρὰ <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Παίδεσσι\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Παίδεσσι\">Παίδεσσι</span></span> καὶ <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ἄννᾳ\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἄννᾳ\">Ἄννᾳ</span></span>  <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Μαιῶρος Καικιλίας\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Μαιῶρος\">Μαιῶρος</span>  <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Καικιλίας\">Καικιλίας</span></span> Ἀρτεμιτίου ει´ <br id=\"al5-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Λούκιος Κορνήλιος Ἀκυίλας\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"praenomen\" data-text=\"Λούκιος\">Λ(ούκιος)</span>  <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"nomen\" data-text=\"Κορνήλιος\">Κορνήλιος</span>  <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"cognomen\" data-text=\"Ἀκυίλας\">Ἀκυίλας</span></span> ὑπὲρ ἑατοῦ καὶ <br id=\"al6-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ποίλλας Κορνηλίας\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ποίλλας\">Ποίλλας</span>  <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κορνηλίας\">Κορνηλίας</span></span> τᾶς ματρὸς καὶ <br id=\"al7-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">7</span>ὑπὲρ <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Μουστίας Οὐολουμνίλλας\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Μουστίας\">Μουστίας</span>  <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Οὐολουμνίλλας\">Οὐολουμνίλλας</span></span> τᾶς <br id=\"al8-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">8</span>ἰδίας γυναικός <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ἀπόλλωνι\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἀπόλλωνι\">Ἀπόλλωνι</span></span> καὶ <br id=\"al9-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">9</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Παίδοις\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Παίδοις\">Παίδοις</span></span> καὶ <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Ἄννᾳ\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἄννᾳ\">Ἄννᾳ</span></span>  <span dir=\"ltr\">(vac.1)</span> ἔνυπτρον ἀνέθηκε </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\">l.5 reg., orig. ἑατοῦ</p>"
